WEBVTT

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:30.256
And hundreds of millions
are facing exploitation

00:05:30.280 --> 00:05:32.320
and abuse, and violence.

00:05:33.360 --> 00:05:37.376
Every seven minutes,
an adolescent boy or girl

00:05:37.400 --> 00:05:41.120
somewhere in the world
is killed by an act of violence.

00:05:43.400 --> 00:05:44.776
And girls are telling me

00:05:44.800 --> 00:05:48.096
that they're especially worried
about their futures.

00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:50.776
And sadly, they're right, too.

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:53.856
Girls face prejudice and discrimination.

00:05:53.880 --> 00:05:55.896
They face early childhood marriage

00:05:55.920 --> 00:05:59.320
and they face life-threatening
early pregnancy.